    Class Description
    CommentAdapter

    CustomSnippetAdapter
    CustomSnippetAdapter makes the snippets look pretty.
    LocationActivity
    The Location activity takes the location layout and passes in the TextView, FilmLocation, Production, and UserComment.
    LoginActivity
    Uses Google Sign-In to allow users to login to application.
    MapsActivity
    This is the primary activity for the application.
    SelectionDialog
    This is the selection dialog that appears when a user selects "Film" or "Television Series" from the Options menu.
    SubmitDialog
    Dialog fragment for users to upload and submit changes.
